<p>Dear <%= @client.name %>,</p>

<p>We are pleased to inform you that your task, "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>", has been successfully created on GigHive.</p>

<p><strong>Task Details:</strong></p>
<table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px;">Description:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px;"><%= @task.description %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px;">Budget:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px;"><%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK ") %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px;">Deadline:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px;"><%= @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px;">Status:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px;"><%= @task.status.capitalize %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>Should you have any questions or require assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

<p>Thank you for choosing GigHive.</p>